This is how to largest_divisor of n:
   Remember that d is diff of n and 1
   Do this n times:
      When d is 1, then:
         The answer is 1
      End when
      When remainder of n and d is 0, then:
         The answer is d
      End when
      Remember that d is diff of d and 1
   End do
   The answer is 1
Now you know